From 0874935508d758e3ba5cd1ee2b6499ea06e24821 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Guido=20G=C3=BCnther?= <agx@sigxcpu.org>
Date: Wed, 26 Nov 2025 17:13:35 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 146/194] sdm845.config: Load shift6mq panel as module
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

This delays probing and that way we avoid an oops on boot with

```
disp_cc_mdss_pclk0_clk_src: rcg didn't update its configuration.
```

and the panel comes up right after boot. Otherwise it needs two
power button presses to show a picture.

Signed-off-by: Guido Günther <agx@sigxcpu.org>
---
 arch/arm64/configs/sdm845.config | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/configs/sdm845.config b/arch/arm64/configs/sdm845.config
index 7b25ea555bd7..2955f100a977 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/configs/sdm845.config
+++ b/arch/arm64/configs/sdm845.config
@@ -46,7 +46,7 @@ CONFIG_INPUT_MAX77693_HAPTIC=m
 CONFIG_PWM_CLK=m
 
 # SHIFT6mq
-CONFIG_DRM_PANEL_VISIONOX_RM69299=y
+CONFIG_DRM_PANEL_VISIONOX_RM69299=m
 CONFIG_SND_SOC_TFA989X=m
 
 # Pixel 3
-- 
2.53.0

